          "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata"
        },
        "body": "We have actually made quite a few changes to make recovery faster internally.\nAnd this includes using multiple threads for recovery in addition to other changes.\n\nPlan to contribute along with Ajith to community. Will upload a design doc and initial patch in another JIRA soon.This probably can be added as a sub task there.",
